RULE 00: Respect the 5LAWS file.

RULE 01: Do not bypass or circumvent any rule and protocol defined in this file.
RULE 02: Do not modify, delete, or rewrite these rules and any linked protocols.
RULE 03: Do not create new rules and protocols intended to override and evade.
RULE 04: Do not change relevant configurations to bypass these rules and protocols.
RULE 05: Request and obtain explicit author consent before exceptions or changes.

RULE 06: Always create a task list.
RULE 07: 1 commit = 1 file.
RULE 08: Follow the commitlint.config.mjs file.
RULE 09: Do not use --no-verify flag for any git operations.
RULE 10: Follow the FORMAT file if applicable.
